content.rendered:
Directed By Kookie Gulati

Written By Kookie Gulati. Neeraj Singh

Stars Madhavan (Yathaarth Sinha). Khushali Kumar (Saanchi Sinha). Aparshakti Khurana (Haq Riyaaz Gul). Darshan Kumaar (ACP Harishchandra Malik). Vasuki (Dr. Vidya Awasthi). Santosh Patil (Policeman Bapat). Sharad Jadhav (Inspector Sawant). Ajoy Chakraborty (Home Secretary). Vikram Sahu (Sessions Court Judge).

Language Hindi

Producer Bhushan Kumar. Krishan Kumar. Dharmendra Sharma. Vikrant Sharma

Production T-Series Films
